dcterms:creator: T. G. Dietterich
dcterms:description: The Taxi domain is a grid-world environment where a taxi must pick up and drop off passengers at designated locations while navigating around walls. It serves as a benchmark for testing reinforcement learning algorithms.
dcterms:title: Taxi domain

dcterms:description: Pitfall is a video game where the player controls a character navigating through obstacles to collect points within a time limit. The game features deterministic transitions and requires strategic movement to avoid hazards.
dcterms:title: Pitfall videogame
